title: The Stone
description:
I present to you the complete studio discography of the amazing Serbian black metal band "The Stone". 
Couldn't find an apparent source for their albums so here you go.
Figure any fans of black metal out there will be able to appreciate this band, even though most of the lyrics are in Serbian (they are awesome lyrics, man).

If you like the band and are somewhere near in the region, come to one of their shows sometime.
Fuckity bye
